---

This repository analyzes the "Primary Human CD4+ T Cell Perturb-seq" dataset
(Zhu, Dann, ... Pritchard, Marson et al., bioRxiv 2025), which is distributed
by its authors under the MIT License. The supplementary data tables under
`suppl_tables/` originate from https://github.com/emdann/GWT_perturbseq_analysis_2025
and remain subject to the original dataset's license and Acceptable Use Policy.
This code (the integration pipeline, figures, validator, and baseline) is the
work of this repository's author under the MIT License above.
